Card XML format
Faction XML format

Implement a combined RPC and event protocol

RPC API:

RegistrationResult Register(string username, string password)
bool Authenticate(string username, string password)
PlayerInfo GetPlayerInfo(playerId): for playerId == null it returns information about the owner of the session 

List<Deck> GetDecks()
int CreateDeck(string name)
void RenameDeck(int deckId, string name)
void ModifyDeck(int deckId, List<DeckCard> cards)
void RemoveDeck(int deckId)
void ActivateDeck(int deckId)

void CreateCustomGameLobby(string name, string password): password == null means it's a public game, the name of a game is a unique identifier
List<CustomGameLobby> GetCustomGameLobbies()
void JoinCustomGameLobby(string name, string password)
void LeaveCustomGameLobby()
void StartCustomGame()

Events:

PlayerJoinedCustomGameLobby(PlayerInfo player)
PlayerLeftCustomGameLobby(PlayerInfo player)
GameLobbyRemoved()